  [Text] The United Nations' World Food Program [WFP] in 
Liberia is suspending its deliveries of food aid to Tubmanburg, 
the headquarters of the divided ULIMO [United Liberation 
Movement for Democracy in Liberia] faction. A WFP spokesman 
