home and abroad have sent messages of congratulations and best 
wishes to the president-elect, Mr. Bakili Muluzi, in the 
presidential election. 
  In his message, the president of the United Front for 
Multiparty Democracy, UFMD, Mr. (Edward Nchika), cautioned Mr. 
