Forces for the Liberation of Angola Military Command in the 
area, concerned with such a tremendous violation of the UN 
charter, today requested that a UN Angola Verification Mission-2 
commission be urgently sent to N'Dalatando to investigate the 
matter. An officer of that command said that a government cannot 
be allowed to massacre thousands of citizens in the name of 
