Network </F>

<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The office of the president and cabinet [OPC] has 
announced that all boards of parastatal organizations in the 
country have been dissolved with immediate effect. In a press 
release issued in Lilongwe, the OPC said new board members will 
be appointed in the near future. The announcement said during 
the interim period, parastatal organizations should contact the 
Department of Statutory Bodies on any matters which would have 
been dealt with by the board. 

</TEXT>

