<F P=100> REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA </F>
<H3> <TI>   PAC Not Opposed to Ingonyama Land Held in Trust </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PAC Not Opposed to Ingonyama Land Held in Trust </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB2205164994 Johannesburg SAPA in English 1352 GMT 22 May 94 </F>
