  [Text] The president, Flight Lieutenant Rawlings, has 
nominated Major Emmanuel Tetteh, MP, as the Eastern Regional 
minister to replace Mr. Paul Kofi Peprah, who is also an MP. 
Maj. Tetteh is currently deputy minister of agriculture, in 
charge of fisheries. The president has also relieved Mr. J.E. 
