ministry, moves to the Ministry of Transport and Communications 
to take over from Mr. P.K. Owusu, MP, as deputy minister. The 
statement also announced the appointment of Nana Adade-Bekoe, a 
former district secretary for the Afram Plains, as the acting 
director of the National Mobilization Program. He replaces Mr. 
Kofi Poturphy, who has been assigned to the National Disaster 
Relief Committee. 

