  [Text] Afonso Dhlakama, leader of the Mozambique National 
Resistance [Renamo], has urged the residents of Pebane District, 
Zambezia Province, to forget about the war. Addressing a mass 
rally in Pebane yesterday, Dhlakama guaranteed that war will 
