forthcoming multiparty elections. Dhlakama, who has been in 
Quelimane since 20 May, is scheduled to close Renamo's political 
conference, which has been discussing particularly issues linked 
to the electoral process. The conference was attended by Renamo 
political delegates in Zambezia and Nampula Provinces. 

