recently, and it is in view of his talks with President Itamar 
Franco that I have come from Lisbon to Luanda with a high-level 
delegation from Brazil for talks on Angola's debt to Brazil. 
Obviously, President Itamar Franco urged us to accommodate the 
Angolan and Brazilian interests, and that is what I am doing. I 
