  [Text] The Mozambique National Resistance [Renamo] has just 
authorized the Provincial Elections Commission in Sofala to 
establish electoral commissions in the Districts of Muanza, 
Chiringoma, and Maringue. A team made up of members of the 
Provincial Elections Commission from Renamo, the government, and 
UN Operations in Mozambique left for Muanza and Chiringoma today 
