  [Text] Harare May 24 SAPA -- Zimbabwe has welcomed South 
Africa's admission into the Organisation of African Unity, the 
ZIANA news agency reported. In a statement on Tuesday, the 
Foreign Affairs Ministry said Zimbabwe welcomed the admission of 
Pretoria into the OAU "as the true fulfilment of the objectives 
